{"tid":31854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[職權當人情]市長以情婦名字命名街道!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2016-12-10T01:40:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T17:34:08.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e3316abf809f67479a0a122a21c2c257857bdc","tid":31854,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T01:40:09.000Z","msg":"以色列一名前市長約瑟涉及連串醜聞，還拿情婦的名字作為街道名稱，周一被定罪。 <br />\n<br />\n特拉維夫地方法院周一裁定約瑟非禮、欺詐和違反信託等16項罪名成立。起訴書詳述數十名在市政府工作的婦女遭性騷擾，以及因拒絕他追求而被革職。 <br />\n<br />\n約瑟是奧爾耶胡達的前市長，他同時被控向接受其追求的女性提供福利。他的其中一個不法行為，是在2013年命名一條新街道為&ldquo;巴厘街&rdquo;。當時他未就提議作出解釋，但起訴書說，這是他給其中一位情婦的暱稱。 <br />\n<br />\n當地傳媒說，市政名稱委員會建議將&ldquo;巴厘街&rdquo;改名，以著名的已故總理梅厄夫人命名為&ldquo;戈爾達．梅厄街&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"e2f4422898c44d6cce33e37a3fd6a94f6aea6687","tid":31854,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T01:43:59.000Z","msg":"強國真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n猶太人就唔會咁自私<br />\n民族性優秀"},{"pid":"a3d3c54e1a28ee7215c2ee121f298bae6b4cd601","tid":31854,"uid":18604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T01:48:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>強國真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n猶太人就唔會咁自私<br />\n民族性優秀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曲直難分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50e757d83376317f0ed0b1bdc1badbea39f38b1","tid":31854,"uid":11021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T01:51:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>強國真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n猶太人就唔會咁自私<br />\n民族性優秀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曲直難分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都分唔到你唔應該上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"718376fa7d5e84b8af6dc1fd344150